amo]] |\ngoals1 = [[Jovan Kirovski|Kirovski]] {{goal|4}} <br> [[Clint Mathis|Mathis]] {{yel|17}}  |\ngoals2 = [[Paul Dalglish|Dalglish]] {{goal|10}} <br> [[Ricardo Clark|Clark]] {{yel|17}} <br> [[Paul Dalglish|Dalglish]] {{goal|21}} <br> [[Brian Mullan|Mullan]] {{goal|71}} |\n|stadium = [[Robertson Stadium]]<br>[[Houston, Texas]]\n|attendance = 23,107\n|referee=Brian Hall\n|report= [http://www.mlsnet.com/news/mls_news.jsp?ymd=20061105&content_id=77871&vkey=news_mls&fext=.jsp Report]\n}}\n\n''[[Houston Dynamo]] advances 3\u20131 in single elimination.''\n\n----\n\n===[[MLS Cup 2006]]===\n\n{{football box |\ndate = November 12, 2006 |\nteam1 = [[Houston Dynamo]] |\nscore = 1\u20131 ([[Extra time|AET]])|\nreport= [http://www.mlsnet.com/news/team_news.jsp?ymd=20061112&content_id=78553&vkey=news_hou&fext=.jsp (Report)] |\nteam2 = [[New England Revolution]] |\ngoals1 = [[Brad Davis (soccer)|Davis]] {{yel|23}}<br />[[Ryan Cochrane (soccer)|Cochrane]] {{yel|99}}<br />[[Craig Waibel|Waibel]] {{yel|103}}<br />[[Brian Ching|Ching]] {{goal|114}}|\ngoals2 = [[Joe Franchino|Franchino]] {{yel|16}}<br />[[Taylor Twellman|Twellman]] {{goal|113}}|\nstadium = [[Pizza Hut Park]]<br>[[Frisco, Texas]] |\nattendance = 22,427 |\nreferee = Jair Marrufo |\npenalties1 =[[Kelly Gray|Gray]] {{pengoal}}<br />[[Stuart Holden|Holden]] {{pengoal}}<br />[[Dwayne De Rosario|De Rosario]] {{pengoal}}<br />[[Brad Davis (soccer)|Davis]] {{penmiss}}<br>[[Brian Ching|Ching]] {{pengoal}}|\npenaltyscore = 4\u20133 |\npenalties2 ={{pengoal}} [[Shalrie Joseph|Joseph]]<br />{{pengoal}} [[Matt Reis|Reis]]<br />{{penmiss}} [[Pat Noonan|Noonan]]<br />{{pengoal}} [[Taylor Twellman|Twellman]]<br />{{penmiss}} [[Jay Heaps|Heaps]]|\n}}\n\n''The [[Houston Dynamo]] win [[MLS Cup]] 4\u20133 on penalties.''\n\n==Team awards==\n\n*'''[[MLS Cup]]:''' [[Houston Dynamo]]\n*'''[[U.S. Open Cup]]:''' [[Chicago Fire S.C.|Chicago Fire]]\n*'''[[MLS Supporters' Shield]]:''' [[D.C. United]]\n*'''[[MLS Reserve Division]]:''' [[Colorad