p Development award for Oberoi Garden City |work=NDTV Property Awards 2017}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://rustomjeespaces.wordpress.com/2013/05/27/winners-of-realty-plus-excellence-awards-2013-west-announced-in-mumbai/|title=Integrated Township of the Year award for Oberoi Garden City |work=Realty Plus Excellence 2013}}</ref>. The development includes a mixed-use building comprising of a five-star hotel, The [[Westin]] Mumbai Garden City and Commerz a premium commercial office space; a first retail destination on the western side of Mumbai, Oberoi Mall; an IB School, [[Oberoi International School]] along with Commerz II which is a GOLD LEED-certified building. The project also includes [[residential developments]] such as Oberoi Seven, Oberoi Woods, Exquisite and Esquire. The company will be launching the 3rd phase of this project very soon.\n\n*[[Three Sixty West]], [[Worli]], is the first uber-luxury project developed by Oasis Realty - JV between Oberoi Realty and Sahana group; it is currently under construction. The development comprises of two towers - one houses The [[Ritz-Carlton Hotel]], and the other has luxury residences managed by The Ritz-Carlton.\n\n*Sky City by Oberoi Realty is a project being developed on a 25-acre land at [[Borivali]] East; bought from [[Tata Steel]] for Rs.1155 crores in 2014. The project will include multiple residential towers, a mall, and a hotel and is very close to the upcoming metro station.\n\n*Oberoi Realty also acquired a 60-acre land parcel from [[GlaxoSmithKline Pharmaceuticals]] in 2019 for Rs.890 crores that is yet to be launched.\n\n*Oberoi Splendor, a residential complex in [[Andheri East]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.moneycontrol.com/news/ipo-issues-open/oberoi-realty-to-complete-4-major-parcelsnext-5-yrs_489175.html|title=Oberoi Realty to complete 4 major parcels in next 5 yrs|website=www.moneycontrol.com|access-date=2016-07-20}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.oberoirealty.com/properties-in-andheri/oberoi-splendor#!awards-and-accolades|title=Properties in Andheri  {{!}} Flats in Andheri East Mumbai {{!}} Oberoi Splendor|website=www.oberoirealty.com|access-date=2016-07-20}}</ref>\n\n*[[Three Sixty West]], the second tallest tower in India, is developed by Oberoi Realty.<ref>http://skyscrapercenter.com/create.php?list_status=COM&status_COM=on&status_UC=on&status_UCT=on&status_DEM=on&list_city=IN-BOM&search=yes</ref>\n\n==Awards==\n\n=== 2019 ===\n*Award for Three Sixty West under the category of '''Mixed-Use Development''' by Asia Pacific Property <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://propertyawards.net/asia-pacific-2019/|title=Three Sixty West wins Mixed-Use Development award|work=Asia Pacific Property 2019}}</ref>\n*Award for Esquire under the category of '''Residential High-Rise Development, India''' by Asia Pacific Property<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://propertyawards.net/asia-pacific-2019/|title=Esquire wins Residential High-Rise Development award|work=Asia Pacific Property 2019}}</ref>\n*'''Best Investor Relations Team (Mid-Cap), Oberoi Realty''' by IR Magazine Awards - India<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://events.irmagazine.com/indiaforum/wp-content/uploads/sites/76/2019/06/India-Awards-2019-Nominees-and-winners-V2.pdf|title=Oberoi Realty wins Best Investor Relations Team (Mid-Cap) award|work=IR Magazine Awards-India 2019}}</ref>\n*Achievement Award for '''Construction Health, Safety & Environment, Sky City''' by CIDC Vishwakarma Awards<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.cidc.in/support/11thVishwakarma/Awardees%20List_11th%20VKA%202019%20(Final).pdf|title=Sky City wins Construction Health, Safety & Environment award|work=CIDC Vishwakarma Awards 2019}}</ref>\n*Achievement Award for New '''Standards in Construction Health, Safety & Environment, Three Sixty West''' by CIDC Vishwakarma Awards<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.cidc.in/support/11thVishwakarma/Awardees%20List_11th%20VKA%202019%20(Final).pdf|title=Three Sixty West wins for New Standards in Construction Health, Safety & Environment award|work=CIDC Vishwakarma Awards 2019}}</ref>\n*Conferred and honored for Outstanding '''Contribution towards Real Estate Industry, Mr. Vikas Oberoi''' by Marketing Maverick Awards<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.freepressjournal.in/business/marketing-maverick-awards-2019|title=Mr. Vikas Oberoi honored for Outstanding Contribution towards Real Estate Industry|work=Marketing Maverick Awards 2019}}</ref>\n*Recognition for Contribution in the Development of Gated Communities in India, Oberoi Realty by IRECMS Awards<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://adda.io/blog/2019/01/adda-presents-irecms-community-management-india/|title=Oberoi Realty wins Recognition for Contribution in the Development of Gated Communities in India award|work=IRECMS Awards 2019}}</ref>\n*'''Most Respected Real Estate Brand of the Year-India, Oberoi Realty''' by Grohe Hurun Real Estate Awards<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.hurunindia.net/grohe-hurun-real-estate-summit-2018-1?lightbox=dataItem-jt3zyk193|title=Oberoi Realty wins Most Respected Real Estate Brand of the Year-India award|work=Grohe Hurun Real Estate Awards 2019}}</ref>\n\n=== 2018 ===\n*'''Shopping Centre of the Year - Retailer's Choice, Oberoi Mall''' by CMO Asia Award for Excellence in Shopping Malls<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cmoasia.org/cmo-asia-awards.html|title=Oberoi Mall wins Shopping Centre of the Year-Retailer's Choice award|work=CMO Asia Awards 2018}}</ref>\n*1st Runner-up for '''High Rise Project of the Year, Esquire''' by Construction Week India Awards<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.constructionweekawards.in/winners|title=Esquire wins 1st Runner-up for High Rise Project of the Year award|work=Construction Week India Awards 2018}}</ref>\n*'''Health & Safety Award for Oberoi Garden City - Commerz II''' by High Rise India Summit & Awards<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.businesswireindia.com/tradepass-successfully-concludes-high-rise-india-summit-awards-57126.html|title=Oberoi Garden City Commerz II wins Health & Safety award|work=High Rise India Summit & Awards 2018}}</ref>\n\n=== 2017 ===\n*'''India\u2019s Top Builders for Mr. Vikas Oberoi''' by 12th CW Architect and Builder (CWAB)<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://asappinfoglobal.com/cwab2017/|title=Mr. Vikas Oberoi wins India\u2019s Top Builders award|work=12th CW Architect and Builder 2017}}</ref>\n*'''Real Estate Company of the Year, Oberoi Realty''' by Construction Week India (CWAB)<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://issuu.com/itpmediagroupindia/docs/cw_01_11_2017|title=Oberoi Realty wins Real Estate Company of the Year award|work=Construction Week India 2017}}</ref>\n*Customer Loyalty Awards for '''Best Loyalty Program in Real Estate Sector, Oberoi Realty''' by The Customer Fest Show<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://content.magicbricks.com/property-news/industry-buzz/mumbai-industry-buzz/oberoi-realty-wins-top-honours-at-the-customer-fest-show-2017/90219.html|title=Oberoi Realty wins Best Loyalty Program in Real Estate Sector award|work=The Customer Fest Show 2017}}</ref>\n*'''Excellence In Township Development, Oberoi Garden City''' by NDTV Property Awards<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://thepropertytimes.in/oberoi-realty-has-been-recognised-for-excellence-in-township-development-at-the-prestigious-ndtv-property-awards/|title=Oberoi Garden City wins Excellence In Township Development award|work=NDTV Property Awards 2017}}</ref>\n*'''Real Estate Person of the Year, Mr. Vikas Oberoi''' by Construction Week India<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://issuu.com/itpmediagroupindia/docs/cw_01_11_2017|title=Mr. Vikas Oberoi wins Real Estate Person of the Year award|work=Construction Week India 2017}}</ref>\n\n=== 2016 ===\n*Award for '''Best for Disclosure and Transparency, Oberoi Realty''' by Asiamoney Corporate Governance Poll India<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.globalcapital.com/asia/data/polls-and-awards/2016-results/corporate-governance-poll/india-and-indonesia|title=Oberoi Realty wins Award for Best for Disclosure and Transparency award|work=Asiamoney